    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a motorcar of exceptional pedigree, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle serves as a definitive example of its model, preserved in a state that mirrors its original factory delivery. Every mechanical system operates with precision, complemented by an interior and exterior finish devoid of any discernible wear. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a specimen of unparalleled quality. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its pristine status.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
